If you’re truly dedicated to delving into the mind of Gil Kalai, you might want to consult [Kalai's 3d conjecture](/Kalai's_3_d_conjecture) or the [Entropy influence conjecture](/Entropy_influence_conjecture). They’re probably as dense and unyielding as the man himself.

